Ju-on: The Grudge;;2002;;R;;Horror;;6.7;;Takashi Shimizu;;Megumi Okina,Misaki Itô,Misa Uehara,Yui Ichikawa,Kanji Tsuda,Kayoko Shibata,Yukako Kukuri,Shuri Matsuda,Yôji Tanaka,Yoshiyuki Morishita,Hideo Sakaki,Takashi Matsuyama,Yuya Ozeki,Takako Fuji,Chikara Ishikura,Chikako Isomura,Chiona Ôkuni,Miho Fujima;;In Japan, when the volunteer social assistant Rika Nishina is assigned to visit a family, she is cursed and chased by two revengeful fiends: Kayako, a woman brutally murdered by her husband and her son Toshio. Each person that lives in or visits the haunted house is murdered or disappears.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0364385/